cast.original_title: All Quiet on the Western Front
cast.overview: When a group of idealistic young men join the German Army during the Great War, they are assigned to the Western Front, where their patriotism is destroyed by the harsh realities of combat.
cast.title: All Quiet on the Western Front

details.biography: Walter Rogers was born on April 6, 1906 in Denver, Colorado, USA. He was an actor, known for All Quiet on the Western Front (1930) and Seven Faces (1929). He was previously married to Viola Alice Naething. He died on November 11, 1943 in Orange County, California, USA.
details.name: Walter Rogers
